room_title: Escape room "Escape Earth" by Epic Escape Game in Denver
room_description: You’re an alien. You and your fellow diplomats from the galaxy M82 have been sent to Earth to make first contact with Earthlings. Unfortunately, your ship’s engine malfunctions and you are forced to make a crash landing. When you wake up, you’re trapped in a government lab. The last thing you remember is a soldier dragging your First Officer away and shouting “I’ll be back in an hour for the rest of you!”
